column2: SELECT p.specObjID, p.ra, p.dec, p.z, p.zErr, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr FROM SpecPhotoAll AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specObjID = p.specObjID WHERE  p.ra BETWEEN # AND # AND p.dec BETWEEN # AND # AND p.zWarning=# AND p.class=&&& AND p.subClass=&&& AND p.survey=&&& AND (p.petroMag_r-p.extinction_r) < # AND p.programname=&&&
